io.lettuce.core.tracing

Interface Tracing

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BraveTracing

    public interface Tracing
    Interface declaring methods to trace Redis commands. This interface contains declarations of basic required interfaces and value objects to represent traces, spans and metadata in an dependency-agnostic manner.
    Since:
    5.1
    Author:
    Mark Paluch, Daniel Albuquerque
    See Also:
    TracerProvider, TraceContextProvider
